<article class="row hentry post-259533 to4_article_post type-to4_article_post status-publish has-post-thumbnail category-op-ed tag-disability tag-disability-rights tag-federal-poverty-level-fpl tag-medicaid tag-medicare tag-poverty tag-social-security-disability-insurance tag-universal-basic-income section-economy-and-labor primary_topic-economy" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle">
