<div class="">
<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/denied-disability-applicants-fare-badly-in-the-labor-market/">Denied Disability Applicants Fare Badly in the Labor Market</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">Those denied coverage suffer great economic harm from their disability but nevertheless don’t qualify for benefits. </div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/kathy-ruffing/" itemprop="url" rel="author">Kathy Ruffing</a></span>, </dd>
<dd class="source org" itemprop="sourceOrganization" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Organization"><span itemprop="name"><a href='https://www.cbpp.org/blog/denied-disability-applicants-fare-badly-in-the-labor-market' itemprop='url'>Center on Budget and Policy Priorities</a></span></dd>
</dl>
